00162 /* Unusual number sizes */
00163 /* Cray (UNICOS) native number sizes:
00164     Char = 8 bits, unsigned
00165     Short=64 int=64 long=64 float=64 double=64 bits
00166     Long double=128 bits
00167     Char pointers = 64 bits
00168     Int pointers = 64 bits
00169 */
00170 /* T3D/T3E (CRAYMPP) native number sizes:
00171     Char = 8 bits, unsigned
00172     Short=32 int=64 long=64 float=32 double=64 bits
00173     Long double=64 bits
00174     Char pointers = 64 bits
00175     Int pointers = 64 bits
00176     Big endian, IEEE floating point
00177 */
00178 /* IA64 (IA64) native number sizes:
00179     Char = 8 bits, signed
00180     Short=16 int=32 long=64 float=32 double=64 bits
00181     Long double=64 bits
00182     Char pointers = 64 bits
00183     Int pointers = 64 bits
00184     Little endian, IEEE floating point
00185 */
00186
